  - R: Tier 1 (>120d): 30% discount/donate; Tier 2 (90-120d): 15% discount

**Finding 6: Price Variance & Revenue Leakage**
- Chart: Figure 6.4.1 (Bar chart: top 20 misaligned SKUs by price CV %)
- ORIR structure:
  - O: Top 20 SKUs show unit price CV 16.8% vs acceptable <5%
  - R: POS misconfiguration, variant mix, manual errors, billing glitches
  - I: ‚Çπ512k annual revenue leakage (18% variance √ó 50% downward error assumption)
  - R: POS consolidation, pricing matrix by size, staff training for 99% consistency

