## üèÜ ELITE SECTION 6 SCORING SIGNALS

**What Gets 10/10:**
‚úÖ All 6 findings follow ORIR rigorously  
‚úÖ Every quantified insight supported by CSV data  
‚úÖ ‚Çπ impact clear for each finding (at-risk or opportunity quantified)  
‚úÖ Recommendations phased (immediate/short-term/strategic/long-term)  
‚úÖ Charts annotated with key insights  
‚úÖ Professional narrative flow  
‚úÖ Problem objectives explicitly mapped

**What Gets 5-7/10 (Avoid):**
‚ùå ORIR incomplete (missing Reason or Implication)  
‚ùå Vague findings ("Some products are slow" vs. "23 SKUs DSLS >90 days, ‚Çπ176k inventory")  
‚ùå No quantified impact  
‚ùå Recommendations without timelines or metrics  
‚ùå First-person language  
‚ùå Charts without interpretation

